OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FA University says it refutes claims
OL,8,Fthat staff have been or are being
OL,9,Fthreatened with termination, if they
OL,10,Frefuse to agree to a change in their
OL,11,Fpension scheme.
OL,13,FMembers of the University College
OL,14,FUnion (UCU) at Southampton Solent
OL,15,FUniversity are due to go on strike
OL,16,Fnext week, saying they were forced out
OL,17,Fof their preferred scheme and were
OL,18,Fthreatened with dismissal if they
OL,19,Frefused.
