OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FIt estimates, academic staff at
OL,8,FSouthampton Solent University could be
OL,9,Fup to #10,000 worse off per year in
OL,10,Fretirement.
OL,12,FUCU says University management told
OL,13,Fthe 286 staff to email HR by "close of
OL,14,Fbusiness" if they "object to the
OL,15,Ftransfer" and that their employment
OL,16,Fwould then cease immediately.
