OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe University says it is disappointed
OL,8,FUCU has decided to undertake strike
OL,9,Faction before any formal proposals
OL,10,Frelated to academic pensions have been
OL,11,Fput forward by the University, and
OL,12,Fthat allegations of staff being sacked
OL,13,Fare "completely untrue."
OL,15,FA Southampton Solent University
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "We refute any
OL,17,Fclaim that staff were, or are, at risk
OL,18,Fof having their employment terminated
OL,19,Ffor refusing change.
