OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"The lack of flexibility in pension
OL,8,Fprovision for post-92 institutions
OL,9,Fmeans that, like many universities,
OL,10,FSouthampton Solent is exploring
OL,11,Fnecessary measures to strengthen our
OL,12,Ffinancial sustainability and secure
OL,13,Fjobs.
OL,15,F"We are committed to comprehensive
OL,16,Fengagement with staff, unions and
OL,17,Fother key stakeholders ahead of any
OL,18,Fdecision being taken that would impact
OL,19,Fstaff's pension provision."
