OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FStaff will walk out on Monday 9
OL,8,FFebruary and Tuesday 17 February after
OL,9,F93% of those who voted in the ballot
OL,10,Fbacked strike action on a turnout of
OL,11,F72%.
OL,13,FIn December 2025, the University took
OL,14,Fthe decision to transfer a number of
OL,15,FProfessional Services staff from the
OL,16,FLocal Government Pension Scheme to the
OL,17,FSolent Pension Plan.
