OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FUCU says the move forced them onto a
OL,8,Fscheme that allows the University to
OL,9,Fpay less into staff pensions, leaving
OL,10,Fstaff poorer.
OL,12,FThe university, however, says it was
OL,13,Fdone in the interest of financial
OL,14,Fsustainability, to protect jobs, and
OL,15,Fthat impacted staff were given the
OL,16,Fopportunity to object to the proposed
OL,17,Ftransfer throughout a comprehensive
OL,18,Fconsultation period on the proposal.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
