OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FUCU believes that forcing staff out of
OL,8,Fthe Teachers' Pension Scheme (TPS) and
OL,9,Fonly allowing access to a defined
OL,10,Fcontribution scheme, such as the
OL,11,F'Solent Pension Plan', could lead to
OL,12,Fthe income from their pension being
OL,13,Freduced by approximately a third.
OL,15,FUCU general secretary Jo Grady said:
OL,16,F"Strike action is a last resort for
OL,17,Four members, but we will not stand by
OL,18,Fwhile staff are forced out of their
OL,19,Fpreferred pension scheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
