OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"The vice-chancellor must see sense,
OL,8,Fstart respecting his staff, and begin
OL,9,Fworking with UCU to protect pensions.
OL,11,F"Our members have the full weight of
OL,12,Fthe national union behind them in
OL,13,Fdefending their income in retirement,
OL,14,Fand we urge management to do the right
OL,15,Fthing and change course to avoid
OL,16,Fdisruption on campus."
