OL,3,CUniversity refutes claims staff
OL,4,Cthreatened to be sacked over pension
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FSolent branch president Steve Desmond
OL,8,Fsaid: "By pulling out of the national
OL,9,Fstandard Teachers' Pension Scheme,
OL,10,FSolent is undermining standards across
OL,11,Fthe entire sector.
OL,13,F"Unless Solent abandons these plans,
OL,14,Fit will face serious industrial
OL,15,Fdisruption this month and long-term
OL,16,Fdamage to its reputation."
